overview:
FiveBucker.com is an online $5 marketplace for buyers and sellers to meet and exchange products, services, and digital goods at a fixed rate.

FiveBucker.com has been honed towards freelancers, hobbyist, part-timers, students, and anyone looking to make an additional income. Alternatively, buyers or companies looking for an outsource option can utilize FiveBucker with the plethora of micro jobs offered.

FiveBucker’s interface allows anyone to upload a product description or service to sell, and via the social network marketing tools, further promote their posts to prospective buyers.

Payments are processed at the seller’s request via AlertPay or Paypal.

There are numerous user-friendly features that are available to users on FiveBucker. Regular updates of news and features about FiveBucker.com can be read via the FiveBucker blog.
